{"id":328042,"type":1,"name":"山海經","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/9e/fc/328042_meQnP.jpg","summary":"《山海经》是中国先秦重要古籍，也是一部富于神话传说的最古老的奇书。该书作者不详，现代学者均认为成书并非一时，作者亦非一人。\r\n\r\n山海经内容主要是民间传说中的地理知识，包括山川、地理、民族、物产、药物、祭祀、巫医等。保存了包括夸父逐日、精卫填海、大禹治水等相关内容在内的不少脍炙人口的远古神话传说和寓言故事。\r\n\r\n简介来自百度百科","info":"<li><span>中文名: </span>山海经</li><li><span>别名: </span>Classic of Mountains and Seas</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">别名: </span>Shan-hai Ching</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">别名: </span>山海経</li><li><span>发售日: </span>战国（14卷）/西汉（4卷）</li><li><span>其他: </span>版本复杂，传世版本共计18卷，包括《山经》5卷，《海经》13卷</li><li><span>作者: </span>佚名</li>","collection":{"collect":1,"doing":1},"tags":[{"name":"名著","count":1},{"name":"国产","count":1}],"relations":[{"id":192614,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/de/ea/192614_Scd22.jpg","title":"山海Go","type":"游戏","url":"https://bgm.tv/subject/192614"},{"id":80757,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/3e/82/80757_bB6oe.jpg","title":"山海伏妖录","type":"游戏","url":"https://bgm.tv/subject/80757"},{"id":326898,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/f5/2e/326898_1Qv6V.jpg","title":"鬼谷八荒","type":"游戏","url":"https://bgm.tv/subject/326898"},{"id":324792,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/16/7f/324792_4yqiQ.jpg","title":"妄想山海","type":"游戏","url":"https://bgm.tv/subject/324792"},{"id":306178,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/d4/21/306178_0rF2F.jpg","title":"山海镜花","type":"游戏","url":"https://bgm.tv/subject/306178"},{"id":258048,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/b7/f1/258048_lEfma.jpg","title":"山海异闻录（手机游戏）","type":"游戏","url":"https://bgm.tv/subject/258048"},{"id":229525,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/7a/b6/229525_ML3J5.jpg","title":"山海宝贝","type":"动画","url":"https://bgm.tv/subject/229525"},{"id":147534,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/42/ae/147534_lssEz.jpg","title":"天眼传奇","type":"动画","url":"https://bgm.tv/subject/147534"},{"id":234080,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/5e/d4/234080_7PrsB.jpg","title":"观海策","type":"动画","url":"https://bgm.tv/subject/234080"},{"id":241665,"imag